<br>
I am pretty sure most people in AD don't particulary like me. I might have many reputations, but a PK sympathiser hasn't been one of them ever. I have been fighting DB, LV and now The Curse pretty much every day I play EQ. Whatever the &quot;PROOF&quot; of my associations with PKers MiM has, I would like to see it for myself.<br>
<br>
For myself, I am completely sure it is another provocation by MiM that promised me I would quit EQ/RZ/Sell/Turn PK in 2 weeks about 3 months ago. Since then they tried their absolutely best to make this game not fun for me and a lot of my friends and quite frankly failed. We fight PKers, we have fun and we still on RZ.<br>
<br>
I am not here to accuse and point fingers. There are some people in AD that would like to KoS me just because they have friends in MiM. I understand that, but by KoSing me without proof, you actually helping The Curse.<br>
<br>
I would like to be cleared from KoS status unless MiM actually manages to produce a proof of me &quot;helping&quot; the PKers. Would be nice if people that try to use their guild's power to settle personal scores weren't so blatant, but I will live.<br>
<br>
Thank you for your time.<br>
<br>
Sadko Skald <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/bascension10244.showUserPublicProfile?gid=moffonfurryhealer>Moffon Furryhealer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 663<br> <font color=#333333>(5/28/03 3:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fascension10244frm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=243.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sadko's status</span><hr size=1> How you gonna be all sarcastic to the people you are asking not to kill you.<br>
