e> Grym is a MiM member?</span><hr size=1> If so, why does he speak for AD members? They can't speak for themselves?<br>
<br>
Someone said to me earlier that it's impossible to prove that anyone has associated with PKers. I would disagree with that.<br>
<br>
When I was an OM member, we stumbled upon a screenshot on LV website of OM officer (Elmorth) being ganked by a group of LV. The odd thing was that in that group of LV was a member of IE/MiM Eisen who in GD was saying in group &quot;you need to malo&quot;. A screenshot like that in MY opinion would be a sufficient proof that a person is aiding/helping/hanging with PKers. I will go ahead and remind all how it ended. MiM said Eisen is innocent because he wasn't PKing Elmorth. He simply buffed a full group of PKers in Bazaar with grp buffs (he never heard of /tgb on) and went AFK. Got ported to GD and came back when LV dropped Elmorth. And just answered to PKer's bitching how they couldn't root Elmorth. Note, MiM in that case said that Eisen was innocent and his explanation was accepted by everyone. IMHO such screenshot would be sufficient to prove someone is pker.<br>
<br>
Another instance. We were farming gems in SG when we saw 2 MiM and DB wizard Once in zone. When we succored out we saw Zayda and Isildr sitting next to Once. We killed Once. Later on when Tempra brought that incident up, MiM claimed Once wasn't in range to MiM (he was) then simply said they didn't care and etc. Note, theres once again a screenshot clearly showing Zayda/Isildr/Once cuddling together in SG. I would argue that such screenshot would be if not proof, then at least evidence.<br>
<br>
Want another one? A few ago I zone into PoV and start chasing Feneris from zone in to stone out. After few zone outs, Ashrael (shoon) zones in and starts nuking me while Feneris is attacking me. I make them both zone at about 1 bubble and come out to PoV. Feneris (I think) goes AFK and after I tell Ashrael what I think if his pvp skills, I see shoon porting Feneris out. I remember seeing Gadi and few others there and they can prove authenticity of my screenshot.  Fact that someone groups pkers for pvp or trusts them enough to get PORTS, not teleports from them is kind of suspicious, don't you think? So that could be counted as evidence.<br>
<br>
Gloryia said she has several screenshots of MiM uniting with PKers to attack her, and quite honestly I believe her.<br>
<br>
Yes, there are honest mistakes and explanations for a lot of things. May be Feneris grouped shoon for a group buff of some kind that I am not aware of (hes a rogue after all). But once again, those things if don't PROVE something at least give reasonable reason for suspicion and give a person chance to explain themselves or their actions.<br>
<br>
What MiM does is nothing but low slander. &quot;Someone somewhere at some point said that some members of doz might have aided or been aided by some pkers&quot;. That is not what I would call a reasonable accusation. That is slander and BS.<br>
<br>
Give me names, ocasions, times. Get screenshots. Who, when, how, against whom. Then I can investigate those allegations, find out for myself if they are true or not and give my friends a chance to defend themselves against those.<br>
<br>
FYI, if required, I can post or refer to all above screenshots and incidents. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/bascension10244.showUserPublicProfile?gid=alurarz>Alura RZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#333333>(5/28/03 10:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fascension10244frm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=243.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grym is a MiM member?</span><hr size=1> Is Tomh the pk in Doz?  Someone in guild said that they guildstated Tomh and he was tagged doz.  Not sure if this is true. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/bascension10244.showUserPublicProfile?gid=alurarz>Alura RZ</A> at: 5/28/03 10:13:24 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/bascension10244.showUserPublicProfile?gid=barmaley>Barmaley</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#333333>(5/28/03 10:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fascension10244frm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=243.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Where are screenshots Ubertanka?</span><hr size=1> Post screenshots of ME helping The Curse which YOUR guild swore they had. If you read my post, I asked for &quot;PROOF&quot; not random slander.<br>
